<list>

<item xml:id="a1">
<locus target="#188r"/>
<desc type="DonationNote"/>
<q xml:lang="gez">ዘንተ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ነገሥት፡ በፃዕኩ፡ አነ፡ ዐምደ፡ ጽዮን፡ ንጉሥ፡ ወስመ፡ መንግሥትየ፡ ገብረ፡ መስቀል፡ ንጉሠ፡
ኢትዮጵያ፡ ለእግዝእትየ፡ ማርያም፡ ለኢየሩሳሌም፡ ከመ፡ ታስተስሪ፡ ሊተ፡ ኀበ፡ ፍቁር፡ ወልዳ፡ አመ፡ ይመጽእ፡ በስብሓቲሁ፡ ከመ፡ ይረሲ፡ ማኅደርየ፡
ምስለ፡ ቅዱሳኒሁ፡ ወኅሩያኒሁ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።</q>
<q xml:lang="en" type="translation">I, king <persName role="donor" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS1854Amdase">ʿAmda Ṣǝyon</persName>, my regnal name Gabra Masqal, king of Ethiopia, have donated this Book of Kings
as a votum to our Lady Mary to Jerusalem, so that she may intercede for me with her beloved Son, when he comes in his glory, to arrange
my dwelling place with his saints and chosen. For ever and ever. Amen.</q>
</item>

<item xml:id="a2">
<locus target="#188v"/>
<desc type="Supplication"/>
<q xml:lang="ar">اذكر يا رب عبدك الخاطى يوحنا | وابوه  هارون اموه  مريم واحواته | شاوول وابراهيم</q>
</item>

<item xml:id="a3">
<locus target="#188v"/>
